item.title: Diani Wilderness Tours and Safaris/Logistics
item.description: Diani Wilderness Safaris Diani Wilderness Tours and Safaris has grown to be one of Kenya's fastest growing and most respected ground handling company. When organizing a Tour Package the experience and expertise of the company you choose is vital. Diani Wilderness tours and safaris has been in operation two decade during which time we have researched every aspect of the tourism industry in East Africa. Our vehicles are equipped with VHF radios for easier communication in the parks, wildlife reference books and extra seat pockets for storing of cameras and personal items. The Tour buses and Jeeps allow nine people seated comfortably but we insist on six people on any tour to guarantee every participant a window seat. Our knowledgeable multilingual driver guides will assist you in identifying many animals birds and trees. Our safaris are for those with a spirit of adventure and those who wish to experience a taste of excitement and romance. We combine lodges, permanent tented camps and hotels to give you the very best of East Africa
